[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     48[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     49[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 4 (Aggregate Outcomes):** Python matches pseudocode: compute goal_achievement_rate, median_time_to_goal, intervention_frequency (among successful patients), adverse_event_rate, and confidence tiers (>=20 high, >=10 moderate, >=5 low, else insufficient). Confidence thresholds match exactly.
